sequenceDiagram
    title WASM Plugin Execution with Host API Calls

    participant TR as TriggerRouter
    participant WP as WasmPlugin<br/>(wasm/adapter/adapter.go)
    participant RT as WASM Runtime<br/>(wasm/runtime/module.go)
    participant WASM as WASM Module<br/>(plugin code)
    participant HostAPI as Host API Functions<br/>(hostapi/)
    participant Perms as Permissions
    participant DB as Database
    participant Net as HTTP Client
    participant Sender as SenderAPI

    TR->>WP: HandleEvent(ctx, event)
    WP->>WP: json.Marshal(event) -> eventJSON
    WP->>RT: CallHandleEvent(ctx, eventJSON, configJSON)

    RT->>RT: Instantiate WASM module with host functions
    RT->>WASM: Call export "handle_event"(eventPtr, eventLen, configPtr, configLen)

    Note over WASM: Plugin starts processing event

    rect rgb(240, 248, 255)
        Note over WASM, DB: Host API call: db_query
        WASM->>HostAPI: db_query(querySpecPtr, querySpecLen)
        HostAPI->>Perms: CheckPermission(pluginID, "db:read")
        Perms-->>HostAPI: ok
        HostAPI->>DB: Execute query
        DB-->>HostAPI: rows
        HostAPI->>HostAPI: writeModMemory(mod, resultJSON)
        HostAPI-->>WASM: (resultPtr, resultLen)
    end

    rect rgb(255, 248, 240)
        Note over WASM, Net: Host API call: http_request
        WASM->>HostAPI: http_request(requestPtr, requestLen)
        HostAPI->>Perms: CheckPermission(pluginID, "network:read")
        Perms-->>HostAPI: ok
        HostAPI->>Net: HTTP GET https://api.example.com/data
        Net-->>HostAPI: response
        HostAPI->>HostAPI: writeModMemory(mod, responseJSON)
        HostAPI-->>WASM: (resultPtr, resultLen)
    end

    rect rgb(240, 255, 240)
        Note over WASM, DB: Host API call: db_save
        WASM->>HostAPI: db_save(recordPtr, recordLen)
        HostAPI->>Perms: CheckPermission(pluginID, "db:write")
        Perms-->>HostAPI: ok
        HostAPI->>DB: Upsert record
        DB-->>HostAPI: ok
        HostAPI-->>WASM: (resultPtr, resultLen)
    end

    Note over WASM: Plugin finishes processing

    WASM-->>RT: Return resultPtr, resultLen
    RT->>RT: readModMemory -> resultJSON
    RT-->>WP: resultJSON

    WP->>WP: json.Unmarshal -> EventResponse

    alt TriggerMessenger and Reply non-empty
        WP->>Sender: SendToChat(ctx, channelType, chatID, reply)
    end

    loop For each message in EventResponse.Messages
        WP->>Sender: SendToChat(ctx, msg.ChannelType, msg.ChatID, msg.Text)
    end

    WP-->>TR: EventResponse
